"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"China's GDP growth target for 2024 is set at around 5%, the same as last year. However, analysts warn that reaching this target will be more challenging compared to 2023 due to the economy's struggles with deflation and falling property prices. The prime minister also announced plans to cut import tariffs on advanced technology and increase the military budget by 7.2%.\",            \"english_title\": \"China's Economic Plans for 2024\",            \"translated_version\": \"China quiere que su econom\u00eda crezca un 5% en 2024, lo mismo que el a\u00f1o pasado. Pero los expertos dicen que ser\u00e1 m\u00e1s dif\u00edcil lograrlo que en 2023 debido a problemas con los precios y la econom\u00eda. El primer ministro tambi\u00e9n planea reducir los impuestos de importaci\u00f3n en tecnolog\u00eda avanzada y aumentar el presupuesto militar en un 7.2%.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Planes Econ\u00f3micos de China para 2024\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The United Nations' special envoy reported `reasonable grounds` to believe that members of Hamas committed sexual violence, including rape, during an attack on October 7th. She called for an investigation into allegations of sexual violence by Palestinians against Israeli forces and settlers.\",            \"english_title\": \"UN Report on Sexual Violence\",            \"translated_version\": \"La enviada especial de las Naciones Unidas inform\u00f3 que hay razones para creer que miembros de Hamas cometieron violencia sexual, incluyendo violaci\u00f3n, durante un ataque el 7 de octubre. Pidi\u00f3 una investigaci\u00f3n sobre acusaciones de violencia sexual por parte de palestinos contra fuerzas y colonos israel\u00edes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Informe de la ONU sobre Violencia Sexual\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Indonesia's incoming president, Prabowo Subianto, aims for 8% annual economic growth during his tenure. He plans to privatize firms and broaden the tax base after his inauguration in October, building on the previous economic growth overseen by his predecessor.\",            \"english_title\": \"Indonesia's Economic Goals\",            \"translated_version\": \"El pr\u00f3ximo presidente de Indonesia, Prabowo Subianto, quiere que la econom\u00eda crezca un 8% cada a\u00f1o durante su mandato. Planea privatizar empresas y ampliar la base impositiva despu\u00e9s de asumir en octubre, siguiendo el crecimiento econ\u00f3mico previo de su predecesor.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Objetivos Econ\u00f3micos de Indonesia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Four former Twitter executives are suing Elon Musk for over $128m in severance pay, alleging that he orchestrated their terminations to avoid paying their severance packages. Mr. Musk also faces potential class-action lawsuits from other staff he fired last year.\",            \"english_title\": \"Lawsuit Against Elon Musk\",            \"translated_version\": \"Cuatro ex ejecutivos de Twitter demandan a Elon Musk por m\u00e1s de $128 millones en compensaci\u00f3n, alegando que orquest\u00f3 sus despidos para evitar pagarles. El Sr. Musk tambi\u00e9n enfrenta posibles demandas colectivas de otros empleados que despidi\u00f3 el a\u00f1o pasado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Demanda Contra Elon Musk\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Microsoft is accused by the New York Times of withholding a `groundbreaking new technology`. The tech giant hopes to dismiss a lawsuit claiming that OpenAI, a company it has invested in, illegally copied articles to develop its chatbot. This legal battle marks a significant clash between a big media company and a tech giant.\",            \"english_title\": \"Microsoft's Legal Battle\",            \"translated_version\": \"El New York Times acusa a Microsoft de ocultar una tecnolog\u00eda innovadora. La gran empresa tecnol\u00f3gica espera desestimar una demanda que afirma que OpenAI, una empresa en la que invirti\u00f3, copi\u00f3 ilegalmente art\u00edculos para desarrollar su chatbot. Esta batalla legal representa un gran enfrentamiento entre una gran empresa de medios y una empresa tecnol\u00f3gica.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Batalla Legal de Microsoft\"        }    ]}"